        },
        "subject": "LU-12668 tests: add EC recovery core tests",
        "message": "LU-12668 tests: add EC recovery core tests\n\nAdd tests 51a-53e exercising core EC recovery paths:\n\n- test_51a/b: EOF boundary recovery -- verify data\n  reconstruction at and near file boundaries\n- test_52a/b/c: degradation limits -- confirm correct\n  behavior when multiple stripes are unavailable\n- test_53a-e: read offset and cross-component recovery\n  for sub-stripe, cross-stripe, and cross-component\n  read patterns\n\nGenerated with Claude Code + Tools\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nTest-Parameters: testlist=sanity-ec\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ic78f72e3e3a9b692d20f976a73c4761d4009dc8d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
